{"tid":1946731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普與確診約翰遜通電話　祝願對方早日康復","createTime":"2020-03-27T20:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T09:59:13.000Z","uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f669934e71126bd54b060daaa929642f38de29ae","tid":1946731,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T20:24:35.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普，在英國首相約翰遜確診感染新型冠狀病毒後，與對方通電話，祝願約翰遜早日康復，又說雙方有密切的友誼。<br />\n<br />\n唐寧街首相府說，特朗普與約翰遜同意，繼續在「七大工業國」及「二十國集團」的平台上，與其他國際伙伴緊密合作，抗擊新型肺炎疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517355-20200328.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517355-20200328.htm&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fmvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=694838de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517355-20200328.htm&h=c775004e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517355-20200328.htm</a>"},{"pid":"11fe887b89eccbe8974eaea40c1a771956e71d13","tid":1946731,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T20:39:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"695944747247edf2c34ac737cf118fb9c6abd263","tid":1946731,"uid":50176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T21:12:17.000Z","msg":"下傻架... 會唔會經電話線傳染架..."},{"pid":"4ca3ae84eb704de493fa509b2ec624a7827a43fc","tid":1946731,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"華為5G"}]}